{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "watches-api-collection",
    "name": "🕰️ Watches API Endpoints",
    "description": "Watches API collection with public, networks, and marketplace platform endpoints.\n\n**Endpoints Included:**\n- GET /api/v1/watches (Public - no auth required)\n- GET /api/v1/networks/watches (Networks - requires x-test-user header)\n- GET /api/v1/marketplace/watches (Marketplace - requires x-test-user header)\n\n**Features:**\n- Search by brand, model, reference\n- Filter by category, condition, price\n- Sort options (platform-specific)\n- Pagination with limit/offset\n- Full Swagger/OpenAPI documentation\n\n**Authentication:**\n- Public endpoint: No authentication required\n- Networks/Marketplace: Set authMode to 'mock' (default) or 'jwt' in Postman environment\n",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Public Watches - GET /api/v1/watches",
      "description": "List all watches publicly available (no authentication required). Supports search, filtering, and pagination.",
